'''Womp''' was a derogatory slang term used to describe members of the ratlike [[Ranat/Legends|Ranat]] species. The term was derived from "[[Womp rat/Legends|womp rat]]."<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|III|332|Womp rat}}</ref>

